# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your key.
#
# The app reads live USPTO trademark records through the RapidAPI
# "uspto-trademark" bridge (USPTO's own search backend blocks server-side
# bots, so this is the practical way to query the same data).
#
# How to get a free key:
#   1. Sign up at https://rapidapi.com
#   2. Subscribe (free Basic tier) to "USPTO Trademark" by Pentaclethemes:
#      https://rapidapi.com/pentaclethemes/api/uspto-trademark
#   3. Copy your X-RapidAPI-Key and paste it below.

RAPIDAPI_KEY=your_rapidapi_key_here
